1.0.0 upgrade to latest javascript conventions
  - ecma modules
  - let/const instead of var
  - arrow notation instead of 'function'.
  - new TypeInfo are created by extending TypeInfo
    rather than registering a callback.

0.0.1 adds standard battery of features:
  - default-values
  - repeats
  - exclusives
  - single-character aliases
  - "presets"
  - user-defined types
  - generic "callback" type
  - minimum and maximum constraints

0.0.0 initial release
